title: Affordaplane
description:
The Affordaplane was introduced in 2001 as a simple to build, affordable ultralight. Featuring three axes, full span ailerons, and classic lines, the Affordaplane has gathered a lot of attention since its release. Read on to find out more about the Affordaplane: 

    The Affordaplane is unique among ultralights, as its fuselage is constructed of aircraft grade square aluminum tubing. Gyrocopters have been using this structure for decades, logging thousands of hours of trouble free flying.
